00:17:53.553 --> 00:17:55.020
Senang kami bisa membantu.

00:17:55.020 --> 00:17:56.586
- Terima kasih banyak.
- Terima kasih.

00:17:56.586 --> 00:17:59.786
- Selamat tinggal.
- Selamat tinggal.

